TW-Judgment-cli

This project is an extension pack built on top of opencli.

Upstream project:
- Name: opencli
- Repository: https://github.com/jackwener/opencli
- Package: @jackwener/opencli
- Verified local version during development: 1.5.6
- Upstream license: Apache-2.0

TW-Judgment-cli does not claim to replace the opencli runtime.
Compatibility with opencli is explicitly version-bounded and verified through this repository's compatibility matrix, doctor checks, and smoke tests.
